    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093220/extras/427510e3126d1af8c3b3a3aaf602d0d0.poster.avif?t=1754516461\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093220/extras/427510e3126d1af8c3b3a3aaf602d0d0.webm?t=1754516461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093220/extras/427510e3126d1af8c3b3a3aaf602d0d0.mp4?t=1754516461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><i> </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hope a potato story is a flash-inspired game in the spirit of the 2000s, where you take control of a tiny potato in a quest to slow down a virus-like curse that slowly threatens your people and the potato kingdom. Using your trusty dash and weapons you acquire, you will fight to push back the infection-or at least thin it's ranks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093220/extras/c62bb1426b706a5d538212e2540fa85e.webp?t=1754516461\" width=618 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This game is being developed alongside the community that  plays it. The future of the game will be shaped by what players and the dev team believe is best. Together, we will make it as fun and enjoyable as possible.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093220/extras/69ebae5d959eaad2bb7718aeeffa3b83.webp?t=1754516461\" width=618 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093220/extras/f632f2d53c438338ae6a0537e971c765.poster.avif?t=1754516461\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093220/extras/f632f2d53c438338ae6a0537e971c765.webm?t=1754516461\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3093220/extras/f632f2d53c438338ae6a0537e971c765.mp4?t=1754516461\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The game in full release will feature more than 30 perks more than 8 different weapons Upgrades for set weapons and will be adding more with time and help from the community</p>",
